KUPHAZAMISEKE ukusebenza kwesibhedlela saseLimpompo kuhlaselwa odokotela abathathu. Esibhedlela iLetaba Hospital, kudutshulwe odokotela abathathu balimala kugasela amadoda endaweni abahlala kuyo kulesi sibhedlela izolo ekuseni. “Ziyahlaselwa izikhungo zezempilo eLimpopo, kumele kubekwe amaphoyissa kuzo zonke izibhedlela,” kusho ungqongqoshe wezeMpilo eLimpopo, uDkt Phophi Ramathuba. Amaphoyisa aseLimpopo aseqale uphenyo oluphuthumayo athungatha amadoda amahlanu agasela ehlomile okubikwa ukuthi atshontsha imali, iTV kanye namaselula kule ndawo. Kwelinye igumbi adubula udokotela, agwaza unkosikazi wakhe ngesikhali esicijile. Bathatha enye iTV, ilaptop nemali. Abathathu abalimele baphuthunyiswe esibhedlela. - ANA 